":menuselection:`Insert Effect` will open a sub-menu to allow you to quickly "
"add the :doc:`/effects_and_compositions/video_effects/"
"transform_distort_perspective/transform` or the :doc:`/"
"effects_and_compositions/video_effects/color_image_correction/"
"lift_gamma_gain` effects."
